  body: '3 delves clear a <sprite="dungeon" index=0> dungeon. Each delve costs <sprite="scroll" index=0> Explore and its fight pays only <sprite="xp" index=0> XP; the third win pays a guaranteed reward bundle. Corrupted (flagged) dungeons add +<sprite="doom" index=0>1 every round until cleared.'
